---
title: Lemon and Herb Salmon with bulgur wheat and charred courgette
description: Salmon has a delicate fish that requires careful pairing. The combination of parsley and lemon offers a flavour that's both earthy and bright but won't overpower the dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23__R11_W06_IE_IECCLF12938-2__KB_Main_high-f414f895.jpg
